#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/integration-testing-using-virtual-machines.md:181
msgid ""
"When developing tests or when something breaks, it’s useful to interactively "
"tinker with the test or access a terminal for a machine."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tutorials/nixos/integration-testing-using-virtual-machines.md:183
